analyticscloudcomponentlayoutitem.name: AnalyticsCloudComponentLayoutItem
analyticscloudcomponentlayoutitem.description: Represents the settings for a Wave Analytics dashboard on a standard or custom page.

consolecomponent.name: ConsoleComponent
consolecomponent.description: Represents a custom console component on a section of a page layout.

container.name: Container
container.description: Represents a location and style in which to display more than one custom console component in the sidebars of the console.

customconsolecomponents.name: CustomConsoleComponents
customconsolecomponents.description: Represents custom console components (Visualforce pages, lookup fields, or related lists) on a page layout.

custommetadata.name: CustomMetadata
custommetadata.description: Represents records of custom metadata types.

custommetadatavalue.name: CustomMetadataValue
custommetadatavalue.description: Represents custom metadata values for a custom metadata component.

deploycallback.name: DeployCallback
deploycallback.description: An interface for metadata deployment callback classes.

deploycallbackcontext.name: DeployCallbackContext
deploycallbackcontext.description: Represents context information for a deployment job.

deploycontainer.name: DeployContainer
deploycontainer.description: Represents a container for custom metadata components to be deployed.

deploydetails.name: DeployDetails
deploydetails.description: Contains detailed information on deployed components.

deploymessage.name: DeployMessage
deploymessage.description: Represents result information for the deployment of a metadata component.

deployproblemtype.name: DeployProblemType
deployproblemtype.description: Describes the problem type for an unsuccessful component deploy.

deployresult.name: DeployResult
deployresult.description: Represents the results of a metadata deployment.

deploystatus.name: DeployStatus
deploystatus.description: The result status of a deployment.

feeditemtypeenum.name: FeedItemTypeEnum
feeditemtypeenum.description: The type of feed item in a feed-based page layout.

feedlayout.name: FeedLayout
feedlayout.description: Represents the values that define the feed view of a feed-based page layout. Feed-based layouts are available on Account, Case, Contact, Lead, Opportunity, custom, and external objects. They include a feed view and a detail view.

feedlayoutcomponent.name: FeedLayoutComponent
feedlayoutcomponent.description: Represents a component in the feed view of a feed-based page layout.

feedlayoutcomponenttype.name: FeedLayoutComponentType
feedlayoutcomponenttype.description: Indicates the type of feed layout component.

feedlayoutfilter.name: FeedLayoutFilter
feedlayoutfilter.description: Represents a feed filter option in the feed view of a feed-based page layout. A filter can have only standardFilter or feedItemType set.

feedlayoutfilterposition.name: FeedLayoutFilterPosition
feedlayoutfilterposition.description: Describes where the feed filters list is included in the layout.

feedlayoutfiltertype.name: FeedLayoutFilterType
feedlayoutfiltertype.description: The type of feed layout filter.

layout.name: Layout
layout.description: Represents the metadata associated with a page layout.

layoutcolumn.name: LayoutColumn
layoutcolumn.description: Represents the items in a column within a layout section.

layoutheader.name: LayoutHeader
layoutheader.description: Represents tagging types used for Metadata.Layout.headers

layoutitem.name: LayoutItem
layoutitem.description: Represents the valid values that define a layout item.

layoutsection.name: LayoutSection
layoutsection.description: Represents a section of a page layout, such as the Custom Links section.

layoutsectionstyle.name: LayoutSectionStyle
layoutsectionstyle.description: Describes the possible styles for a layout section.

metadata.name: Metadata
metadata.description: An abstract base class that represents a custom metadata component.

metadatatype.name: MetadataType
metadatatype.description: Represents the custom metadata components available in Apex.

metadatavalue.name: MetadataValue
metadatavalue.description: An abstract base class that represents a custom metadata component field.

minilayout.name: MiniLayout
minilayout.description: Represents a mini view of a record in the Console tab, hover details, and event overlays.

operations.name: Operations
operations.description: Represents a class to execute metadata operations, such as retrieving or deploying custom metadata.

platformactionlist.name: PlatformActionList
platformactionlist.description: Represents the list of actions, and their order, that display in the Salesforce mobile action bar for the layout.

platformactionlistcontextenum.name: PlatformActionListContextEnum
platformactionlistcontextenum.description: Describes the different contexts of action lists.

platformactionlistitem.name: PlatformActionListItem
platformactionlistitem.description: Represents an action in the platform action list for a layout.

platformactiontypeenum.name: PlatformActionTypeEnum
platformactiontypeenum.description: The type of action for a PlatformActionListItem.

primarytabcomponents.name: PrimaryTabComponents
primarytabcomponents.description: Represents custom console components on primary tabs in the Salesforce console.

quickactionlis.name: QuickActionLis
quickactionlis.description: Represents the list of actions associated with the page layout.

quickactionlistitem.name: QuickActionListItem
quickactionlistitem.description: Represents an action in the QuickActionList.

relatedcontent.name: RelatedContent
relatedcontent.description: Represents the Mobile Cards section of the page layout.

relatedcontentitem.name: RelatedContentItem
relatedcontentitem.description: Represents an individual item in the RelatedContent list.

relatedlist.name: RelatedList
relatedlist.description: Represents related list custom components on the sidebars of the Salesforce console.

relatedlistitem.name: RelatedListItem
relatedlistitem.description: Represents an item in the related list in a page layout.

reportchartcomponentlayoutitem.name: ReportChartComponentLayoutItem
reportchartcomponentlayoutitem.description: Represents the settings for a report chart on a standard or custom page.

reportchartcomponentsize.name: ReportChartComponentSize
reportchartcomponentsize.description: Describes the size of the displayed report chart component.

sidebarcomponent.name: SidebarComponent
sidebarcomponent.description: Represents a specific custom console component to display in a container that hosts multiple components in one of the sidebars of the Salesforce console.

sortorder.name: SortOrder
sortorder.description: Describes the sort order of a related list.

statuscode.name: StatusCode
statuscode.description: Describes the status code for an unsuccessful component deploy.

subtabcomponents.name: SubtabComponents
subtabcomponents.description: Represents custom console components on subtabs in the Salesforce console.

summarylayout.name: SummaryLayout
summarylayout.description: Controls the appearance of the highlights panel, which summarizes key fields in a grid at the top of a page layout, when Case Feed is enabled.

summarylayoutitem.name: SummaryLayoutItem
summarylayoutitem.description: Controls the appearance of an individual field and its column and row position within the highlights panel grid, when Case Feed is enabled. You can have two fields per each grid in a highlights panel.

summarylayoutstyleenum.name: SummaryLayoutStyleEnum
summarylayoutstyleenum.description: Describes the highlights panel style for a SummaryLayout.

uibehavior.name: UiBehavior
uibehavior.description: Describes the behavior for a layout item on a layout page.
